item.title: Help.. with complier
item.dc:creator: @inuyasha_12345 inuyasha 12345
item.description:
@inuyasha_12345 wrote:

I had the same problem before!
When i downloaded JDK it only downloaded the jre1.6.0_3 and didnt give me the jdk… Meaning that my javac was not there! How i fixed this problem. Go to www.java.com, go to download JDK like normal, but take the offline 1, then once itrs done downloading that, disconect the internet then double click on the jdk6u3 and it should download with jdk and jre.
